            <description><![CDATA[I am happy to officially introduce Emitbase ‚Äî an open-source alerts platform for developers. It allows you to connect to a database, define the logic of alerts in SQL, and specify channels for alerts (Email or Slack), all configured in declarative YAML files.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I am happy to officially introduce Emitbase ‚Äî an open-source alerts platform for developers. It allows you to connect to a database, define the logic of alerts in SQL, and specify channels for alerts (Email or Slack), all configured in declarative YAML files.</p><div style="text-align:center"><p><img loading="lazy" alt="Emitbase declarative files" src="/emitbase-website/assets/images/emitbase_intro-28a366739c381b9784d76626fa3c89ff.png" width="1000" height="1000" class="img_ev3q"></p></div><p>The vision is to create a simple yet powerful alerting tool. It didn't come out of nowhere; it originated while I was building my last product. I needed a tool that wouldn't interfere with my business logic but would act as a straightforward layer directly above the database, allowing me to define alerting logic. Emitbase is exactly it.</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="eager-for-feedback">Eager for Feedback<a href="#eager-for-feedback" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Eager for Feedback" title="Direct link to Eager for Feedback">‚Äã</a></h2><p>I want to continue with development, but not everything I think is good is actually good. I am launching it with this piece of information in my mind, and I am super eager to receive feedback from the community! If Emitbase caught your attention, check <a href="https://emitbase.github.io/emitbase-website/docs/introduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the introduction</a>, <a href="https://emitbase.github.io/emitbase-website/docs/getting-started" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">try it</a>, and provide me with any feedback on <a href="https://emitbase.github.io/emitbase-website/docs/community/slack" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Slack</a>.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info alert alert--info admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>info</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>If you want to support Emitbase even more, please hit ‚≠êÔ∏è in the <a href="https://github.com/emitbase/emitbase-core" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emitbase repository</a>.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
